ygData.subject: Re: Guild Approved
ygData.msgSnippet: In a message dated 8/5/99 7:58:10 AM Eastern Daylight Time, kerik@geocities.com writes:
ygData.messageBody:
In a message dated 8/5/99 7:58:10 AM Eastern Daylight Time,
kerik@... writes:

<< Hello All,

Good news, our guild is approved. Soon, members of the Mystic Alliance will
be wandering the world of Norrath. Unfortunately, it will take me awhile to
get the
various chapters established on the servers that we need. I will be out of
town Aug. 7 -14 (argh! a whole week without EQ) but on Sunday the 15th, I
hope to get
the chapters set up.

I will be the guildmaster on Brell Serillis, but I will need others to do
the same on the other servers. I know several of you have mentioned you'd be
willing to
do it, so please tell me again if you want to do it, and let me know which
server.

I will attempt to get as many set up on Sunday the 15th, as I can.

Thanks,
David

Dedric, lvl 9 gnome, Necro on Brell
Kerik, lvl 3 High Elf, Enchanter on Brell >>

I would be happy to be the guild master on the Bristlebane server. I dont
however know many GLBT on there. Would also have to be my new char. Lev 7
Half Elf Ranger by the name of Zute. My other two chars are already in
guilds.

I would like to meet some of us on that server. Just look me up when you fell
like it.

Wampir Keogh. lev 25 Dark Elf Necro. <Putrid Soul>
Windom, Lev9 Barbarian Sham. (arnt they gorgus)
Zute, Lev 7 Half Elf Ranger.

All on the bristlebane server

Thanks
Jamie
